  "summary": "Malicious code in myreviews-core (npm)",
  "details": "The package myreviews-core@99.0.0 has no functional code (empty module) and no repository or description. On install, its postinstall script sends the installer's hostname, username, current working directory, and timestamp to webhook[.]site/ac3b6fd3-80b7-41ee-9d43-f8b815959005 via an HTTPS GET request. This is a reconnaissance beacon that collects system metadata for targeting purposes.",
